#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>empty</quote> &GUI; interface, before any extra "
"address books have been created. The <quote>Personal Contacts</quote> "
"address book is present when &kaddressbook; is first installed."
